#DESCRIPTION
#  Interpreting Riemann sums in terms of area
#ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Integrals)
## DBsection(Riemann sums)
## Date(5/10/2008)
## Institution(University of Rochester)
## Author(Paul Pearson)
